TITLE: Memphis mom, 1-year-old abducted outside Target at midday; police hunt suspects
SUMMARY: Memphis Police are looking for two men allegedly involved in the abduction and robbery of a mother and her 1-year-old this week. It happened in a Target parking lot.

TITLE: Tupelo, Mississippi pilot threatening to crash plane into Walmart, police say
SUMMARY: A pilot has threatened to crash into a Walmart in Tuleop, Mississippi authorities warned Saturday as they evacuated the area.

TITLE: Artemis moon launch: Americans weigh in on whether NASA program is worth $93B cost
SUMMARY: Americans sound off on whether they support paying for NASA's Artemis mission objective of landing astronauts on the lunar surface for the first time in decades.

TITLE: Nine migrants found dead at Texas border, 53 apprehended trying to cross Rio Grande
SUMMARY: The bodies of nine migrants were found Thursday and another 53 were caught trying to enter the United States from through the Rio Grande, authorities said.

TITLE: Tupelo, Mississippi pilot who threatened to ram plane into Walmart is down, in custody
SUMMARY: A pilot has threatened to crash into a Walmart in Tuleop, Mississippi authorities warned Saturday as they evacuated the area.

TITLE: Liza Fletcher abduction: Timeline of the Memphis teacher's disappearance
SUMMARY: Here is a timeline of events surrounding the disappearance of.Memphis teacher Eliza Fltecher, who was abducted Friday morning while on a jog near the University of Memphis.

TITLE: Followers of social media spirituality influencer accused of 2 murders in Alabama: 'I am a god'
SUMMARY: Three followers of social media influencer Rashad Jamal and his cult-like group have been accused of two separate murders in Alabama. Jamal is currently in prison.

TITLE: California wildfire sets homes ablaze, forces evacuations
SUMMARY: A California wildfire has threatened northern communities, injuring several people and forcing evacuations. Multiple homes were destroyed in Mill Fire on Friday.
